//TWO'S COMPLEMENT:

    => 9+(-4)=5         ===>      -4 = 00000100 -> 11111011         (inverting all digits and then adding 1 to it)
                                                         +1
     9        00001001                           -------------
  +(-4)      +11111100   <------------              11111100
   ------   ------------             |           -------------
     5        00000101               |                 |
   ------   ------------             |_________________|
   
   
